message.content:
1. A household questionnaire survey was carried out in the trial communities in 2010.
2. The 2010 survey included 12,312 households.
3. Another household questionnaire survey was carried out in the trial communities in 2012.
4. The 2012 survey included 5349 households in intervention clusters.
5. The 2012 survey also included 5142 households in control clusters.
6. The surveys included questions about socio-economic status.
7. The surveys included questions about self-reported dengue illness.
8. The surveys included questions about the purchase of insecticide anti-mosquito products in the previous month.
9. The surveys included questions about the expenditure on insecticide anti-mosquito products in the previous month.

messages.content:
Statement: We carried out a household questionnaire survey in the trial communities in 2010 (12,312 households) and 2012 (5349 households in intervention clusters, 5142 households in control clusters), including questions about socio-economic status, self-reported dengue illness, and purchase of and expenditure on insecticide anti-mosquito products in the previous month.
